# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:11
translate chinese cc11_25d87ee2:

    # pc "Do you think that there are other worlds out there?"
    pc "你觉得外面还有其他世界吗？"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:13
translate chinese cc11_ed533441:

    # sc "Do you mean like aliens?"
    sc "你是说像外星人那样吗？"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:14
translate chinese cc11_97ae54c7:

    # pc "No, like alternate universes."
    pc "不，我是说平行宇宙。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:16
translate chinese cc11_2518c7b6:

    # sc "I don't really know about all that stuff. That's more physics than psychology. Or science fiction."
    sc "那些东西我其实不太懂。那更属于物理学而不是心理学。或者说科幻小说。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:17
translate chinese cc11_00ac60ef:

    # sc "We can talk about delusions though, if you'd like."
    sc "不过如果你愿意的话，我们可以聊聊妄想症。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:18
translate chinese cc11_d27ac593:

    # pc "Are you making fun of me?"
    pc "你在取笑我吗？"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:20
translate chinese cc11_f130e184:

    # sc "I'm sorry. I shouldn't."
    sc "对不起，我不该那样。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:21
translate chinese cc11_1037ea46:

    # pc "I guess you don't believe in alternate universes then?"
    pc "那你大概是不相信平行宇宙吧？"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:23
translate chinese cc11_2cd92d5b:

    # sc "Not really. I feel like it's people being hopeful that there is something else out there."
    sc "倒也不是。我觉得这只是人们对“外面的世界还有其他可能”抱有的希望罢了。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:24
translate chinese cc11_25b69d91:

    # sc "But in the end, I think that there is only one you and you only get one life, so it's best not to waste it by worrying about what else might be out there."
    sc "但归根结底，我认为世上只有一个你，你只有这一生，所以最好别把时间浪费在担心“外面还有什么”上。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:25
translate chinese cc11_b393365f:

    # sc "But I really shouldn't even be saying things like that."
    sc "不过我其实不该说这种话。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:27
translate chinese cc11_7b90b1cf:

    # sc "You believe whatever you want to believe. Whatever makes you happy."
    sc "你信什么都行。只要能让你开心就好。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:28
translate chinese cc11_dde8fcc5:

    # sc "What do I know? I'm just a school counselor."
    sc "我懂什么呢？我只是个学校辅导员。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:29
translate chinese cc11_5abf7872:

    # pc "It's okay. Thanks for being honest."
    pc "没关系。谢谢你的坦诚。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:31
translate chinese cc11_462749ab:

    # sc "Just keep it between us, okay? I could actually get in trouble for saying stuff like that."
    sc "就我们俩知道，行吗？说这种话我可能会惹上麻烦的。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:32
translate chinese cc11_053ddf8f:

    # pc "It'll be our secret."
    pc "这会是我们的小秘密。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:34
translate chinese cc11_0a8cb978:

    # sc "Thanks, [pcname]. You better head to class."
    sc "谢谢，[pcname]。你最好去上课了。"

# game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:36
translate chinese cc11_66b35acb:

    # pc "Okay, talk to you later Gertrude."
    pc "好的，格特鲁德，回头见。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/CounselorChats/Conversations/cc11.rpy:1
    old "To unlock this conversation you have to progress far enough in the main story to have met Whitney."
    new "要解锁这段对话，你必须在主线剧情中推进到足够远，直到遇到惠特尼。"

